HEADWORD: Deedless
<hw>Deed"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not performing, or not having
performed, deeds or exploits; inactive.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Deedless</qex> in his tongue.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Deed poll</ent>⟦br⟧
